    org.conqat.lib.commons.clone.IDeepCloneable, IStateflowElement<IStateflowChartContainer<?>>, IStateflowNodeContainer<IStateflowChartContainer<?>>

    public class StateflowChart
extends StateflowDeclContainerBase<IStateflowChartContainer<?>>
implements IStateflowNodeContainer<IStateflowChartContainer<?>>
    This class represents Stateflow charts. There is a one-to-one association between StateflowBlocks and StateflowCharts.
